    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "In Wuqian, Visit a Buddhist Monk's Green Bamboo Pavillion\n\nOne may
        do without meat in one\u2019s diet, \nBut one cannot live without bamboo.
        \nWithout meat, one grows thin; \nWithout bamboo, one grows vulgar. \nA thin
        man may regain his weight, \nBut a vulgar man cannot be cured. \nOthers may
        laugh at these words, \nFinding them both lofty and foolish. \nIf, in the
        presence of this gentleman, one still feasts heartily, \nHow could there
        ever be a Yangzhou Crane in this world?\n\nSu Dongpo"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5122842465899161861, guid: ed7b740a5cf36044ab197a19d1fe05ab, type: 3}
